DBsheetConfig.query: SELECT value Id, T1.GroupingId, T4.Id Conventions FROM ORE.dbo.ConventionsSwapIndex T1 INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName T2 ON T1.Id = T2.value INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.ConventionsSwap T4 ON T1.Conventions = T4.Id ORDER BY 1 ASC

field.name: *Id
field.lookup: SELECT value Id,value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName ORDER BY value

field.name: *Conventions
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.Id Conventions,!T!.Id FROM ORE.dbo.ConventionsSwap !T! ORDER BY Id
